title: How do I get to board level 7?
body: Not really sure how that works. If it's related to ingame level, I've be 30 forever but have never really been inclined to post on the forums.

replies.body: Your profile should update on its own, but you can also use the[ syncing tool ](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/fos1aFEB-boards-profile-syncing-tool)to help!
